title: Workshop: Drift Diffusion Models (Part II)
description: Yunshu Fan, from the Ding and Gold Labs, is presenting a 2-part workshop to introduce the drift-diffusion model (DDM), a model that is commonly used in modeling decision behavior. The goals are to familiarize participants with the model enough to (1) start to think about whether and when the model can be usedful, and (2) feel less confused when reading about it in literature and talks.
location: 427 Goddard Labs
